U1RvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=699c1f45\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.infoworld.com/article/2612386/mac-os-x/cisco-shows-how-to-manage-35-000-macs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實好多大IT公司都有用Mac。上面4間公司加埋已經係十幾萬部機。"},{"pid":"69e266d5be1a6e5e931d25def8adf8cb97f7c63f","tid":243884,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"avast"},{"pid":"20342b8a301656c28e30ed228d4914923111c84a","tid":243884,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8a97f71caa4d7be374850cf8f632945c9dc9188","tid":243884,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>只要唔用老番<br />\n唔亂裝「破建檔」<br />\n用 time-machine<br />\n<br />\nMac 出事機會細好多，<br />\n<br />\n始終hack Mac得到的「回報」低好多。。。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無咩公司／公營機構用mac</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比例上少公司用Mac但不至於無咩公司用。IBM係Apple最大corporate客。另外Google有數以萬計嘅Mac。Facebook都有萬幾部。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.computerworld.com/article/3131906/apple-mac/ibm-says-macs-are-even-cheaper-to-run-than-it-thought.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.computerworld.com%2Farticle%2F3131906%2Fapple-mac%2Fibm-says-macs-are-even-cheaper-to-run-than-it-thought.html&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1RvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f2c166ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.computerworld.com/article/3131906/apple-mac/ibm-says-macs-are-even-cheaper-to-run-than-it-thought.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://9to5mac.com/2013/11/27/how-google-manages-over-40000-macs-without-much-help-from-apple/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2013%2F11%2F27%2Fhow-google-manages-over-40000-macs-without-much-help-from-apple%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1RvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e8d2a955\" target=\"_blank\">https://9to5mac.com/2013/11/27/how-google-manages-over-40000-macs-without-much-help-from-apple/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blogs.wsj.com/cio/2015/07/17/facebook-a-big-user-of-apple-machines-writes-and-open-sources-its-own-mac-os-security-software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs.wsj.com%2Fcio%2F2015%2F07%2F17%2Ffacebook-a-big-user-of-apple-machines-writes-and-open-sources-its-own-mac-os-security-software%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1RvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b1211c0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://blogs.wsj.com/cio/2015/07/17/facebook-a-big-user-of-apple-machines-writes-and-open-sources-its-own-mac-os-security-software/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCisco有35000部Mac（2013年）。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.infoworld.com/article/2612386/mac-os-x/cisco-shows-how-to-manage-35-000-macs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.infoworld.com%2Farticle%2F2612386%2Fmac-os-x%2Fcisco-shows-how-to-manage-35-000-macs.html&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1RvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=699c1f45\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.infoworld.com/article/2612386/mac-os-x/cisco-shows-how-to-manage-35-000-macs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實好多大IT公司都有用Mac。上面4間公司加埋已經係十幾萬部機。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多同少，係形容詞，唔係一個量詞<br />\n唔洗玻璃心，下下都起角<br />\nMac係少眾，無人會反對<br />\n對比全球商用電腦，Mac少眾更加無得抗辯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年先有一個木馬扮flash, 引誘mac 用戶安裝<br />\n近年攻擊mac的木馬，都係借道 flash 入侵<br />\n<br />\n都係個句，<br />\nMac只要唔用老番，唔用破解檔，唔用flash<br />\n用time-machine backup<br />\n<br />\n出事機會細好多<br />\n<br />\n而且當出現針對mac的攻擊時，<br />\n一定登上所有科技網headline</blockquote><br />\n少眾同系統本身安唔安全冇關係<br />\n就算係少眾仍然會有人去研究 mac os, Linux, Unix 等等既漏洞<br />\n就算今次Wannacry你係Windows 唔用老番唔用破解檔都會中招<br />\n仲有，Mac都有唔用唔老番唔用破解檔都會中既malware <br />\n<a href=\"https://9to5mac.com/2017/04/28/mac-malware-dok/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2Fmac-malware-dok%2F&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1RvwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d7fcc1e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://9to5mac.com/2017/04/28/mac-malware-dok/</a><br />\n<br />\n你所講既方法就只係叫人做多d運動飲食均衡<br />\n但係各種傳染病依然係會揾到你"},{"pid":"4339e1bbcd92ce5aa57822438181daf2ce8d538b","tid":243884,"uid":34154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我用緊mac cleaner 2<br />\n之前唔知邊到dl左隻破解版<br />\n最近佢成日叫我更新但窮撚唔想俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWindows 同 Mac都係用Bitdefender <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75acad00f5b73c0bbbaa00e7f3583153ace00828","tid":243884,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:59:56.000Z","msg":"Mac係少數唔反對。但今次wannacry用嘅漏洞源頭係美國NSA。如果NSA有類似嘅macOS或Linux漏洞我一D唔奇怪。政府做野唔係睇小唔小眾。如果再有人用NSA嘅漏洞牟利，linux同macOS都有可能。<br />\n<br />\n*nix OS比Windows較安全但唔係天下無敵。<br />\n<br />\n另外macOS同Linux都發生過官網俾人入侵（transmission，LinuxMint）植入malware事件，唔用老翻都唔一定絕對安全。"},{"pid":"d6d29b08fb2e8d853b9cc99d9135ed5970829563","tid":243884,"uid":46940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:15:13.000Z","msg":"搭單問 中左mac keeper點解毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774b57ee728d10326835527afef019332216b807","tid":243884,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:20:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5eee9873946f262967b35357afeeda59b67d1773","tid":243884,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:25:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"083860e3ed40fb55d4a6ae96f630d818e504af12","tid":243884,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T18:29:25.000Z","msg":"無錢買mac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}